<!--
=============================================================================
 default/data/ui/views/bitsight_navigation_hub.xml
 BitSight for Splunk App
 Navigation Hub
=============================================================================

PURPOSE

Tile-based landing page linking to the primary BitSight views.

This view uses the established portal-tile navigation design used across
the Splunk apps and organizes navigation by the approved BitSight
section model.

FILE LOCATION

App-relative path
default/data/ui/views/bitsight_navigation_hub.xml

SECTION MODEL

Core Capabilities
Advanced Analytics
Compliance & Governance
Operational Excellence
Alert Actions

TILE LABEL MODEL

Feature titles are used exactly as provided.

VIEW MAPPING MODEL

Tiles link to the delivered BitSight views where applicable.
Capability-only items without a dedicated BitSight view are displayed as
non-clickable tiles.

=============================================================================
-->
